{"word":"G3831 - πανήγυρις - panḗgyris - pan-ay'-goo-ris - General assembly","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">πανήγυρις</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>panḗgyris"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>pan-ay'-goo-ris"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>General assembly"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"சர்வசங்கம் - பெண்பால் பெயர்ச்சொல்"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"1. a festal gathering"},{"paragraph":"2. a public festal assembly"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Noun Feminine / பெயர்ச்சொல் (பெண்பால்)</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> From <a href=\"#/G3956 - πᾶς - pâs - pas/3956\">G3956</a> and a derivative of <a href=\"#/G58 - ἀγορά - agorá - ag-or-ah'/58\">G58</a>; a <i>mass meeting</i>, that is, (figuratively) <i>universal companionship:</i> - general assembly."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"}]}